"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">是该领域一个强有力的竞争者。它与 Bolt 非常相似，都能够快速启动和运行。其突出之处在于其智能的快速操作，可以帮助指导你的下一步行动。当与 Stripe（或 Paypal）集成时，Lovable 的功能非常强大，这使得通过你的产品接收订阅付款或购买变得非常容易。他们最近添加了 Github 同步功能，这意味着如果你想编辑某些内容，你可以克隆你的项目，用你喜欢的工具进行编辑，然后将其推送回 GitHub，之后内容就会同步回 Lovable。对于那些喜欢拥有更多控制权的人来说，这是一种非常有前景的方法。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc5cb6e51\" id=\"uc5cb6e51\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1756041312324-d7c61cce-4e00-478a-9f4d-382b99556192.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9fe5b565-8478-4164-9e7e-ed7070a7ff1%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u78afaade-908e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A330%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A297794%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A659%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22PUBLISH%20CHORE-BUDDY-MOBILE%20HOME%20INVITE%20PURPLE%20COLOR%20SCHEME%2CTASK%20PRIORITIZATION%2CCATEGORIES%2C%20TASK%20BUDDY%20AND%20SMOOTH%20ANIMATIONS%20FOR%20TASK%20COMPLETION.%20WHAT'S%20NEXT%3F%20ALL%20CATEGORIES%20REFINE%20%26%20CUSTOMIZE%3ATWEAK%20THE%20DESIGN%2C%20ANIMATIONS%2CAND%20LAYOUTS%20VIA%20PROMPTS%20OR%20VISUAL%20SEARCH%20TASKS...%20EDITS.%20MASTER%20PROMPTING%3AUSE%5C%22CHAT%20MODE%5C%22TO%20PLAN%20OUT%203%20TASKS%20HIDE%20COMPLETED%20YOUR%20PROJECT%20WITHOUT%20MAKING%20EDITS.USE%20CLEAR%2C%20DETAILED%2CAND%20ITERATIVE%20PROMPTS%20FOR%20BEST%20RESULTS.%20WORK%20COMPLETE%20MOBILE%20APP%20DESIGN%20GITHUB%20SYNC%3ATRANSFER%20YOUR%20PROJECT'S%20CODE%20TO%20FINISH%20THE%20UL%20WIREFRAMES%20AND%20COLOR%20SCHEME%20GITHUB%20FOR%20TWO-WAY%20SYNC%20OF%20EDITS.%20%E7%99%BDMAY%2011%2C2025%20NEED%20TO%20SAVE%20TASKS%2CADD%20USER%20ACCOUNTS%2COR%20CONNECT%20ERRANDS%20BUY%20GROCERIES%20WITH%20OTHER%20SERVICES%3FSUPABABASE%20IS%20A%20SIMPLE%20WAY%20TO%20MILK%2CEGGS%2CBREAD%2CAND%20VEGETABLES%20ADD%20THESE%20FEATURES%