ke-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">：我经常想修复一些东西，结果却把其他东西弄坏了。你可以提示 AI</span></em><em><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u95b8768e\" id=\"u95b8768e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">哪些东西不能碰</span></strong></em><em><span data-lake-id=\"ue5eaf786\" id=\"ue5eaf786\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">！这可以最大程度地减少潜在的损坏！</span></em></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"Zq6z7\" id=\"Zq6z7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9627390b\" id=\"u9627390b\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">控制力较强—— V0（Vercel）</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"ue7fef877\" id=\"ue7fef877\"><span data-lake-id=\"u67ca4253\" id=\"u67ca4253\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">如果你准备超越原型，进入更充实的内容，那么</span><a href=\"https://v0.dev/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u68da5ba9\" id=\"u68da5ba9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0201bcbf\" id=\"u0201bcbf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">V0</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u1c1a330b\" id=\"u1c1a330b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">是一个不错的选择。我对 Vercel 最大的不满在于其免费套餐的限制。Figma 集成也不在其免费套餐内，所以如果你是一位设计师，想要尝试各种可能性，如果不购买其高级订阅服务，这可能会有点困难。V0 设计的一个小亮点是，它们会在主提示体验中展示社区项目，这不仅让你可以从其他项目中获得灵感，还允许你了解项目的底层机制，以便将其应用于自己的项目。这个功能并非 V0 独有，但感觉是最流畅的。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ued0448b4\" id=\"ued0448b4\"><em><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u13d8de47\" id=\"u13d8de47\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">💡</span></strong></em><em><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6b8da79e\" id=\"u6b8da79e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\"> 提示</span></strong></em><em><span data-lake-id=\"u3ab0b2ad\" id=\"u3ab0b2ad\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">：使用 Vibecoding 产品时，PRD 非常有用。它可以包含您想要创建的所有需求和规格。事实上，有一个很棒的产品——ChatPRD，可以帮助您生成一个。然后，您可以将其添加到项目文档中，以指导您的 AI 伙伴。</span></em></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"g6B5A\" id=\"g6B5A\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue0b6b9e9\" id=\"ue0b6b9e9\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">控制力较强—— Replit</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u3726fc4e\" id=\"u3726fc4e\"><a href=\"https://replit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u4ced09fd\" id=\"u4ced09fd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u512a350f\" id=\"u512a350f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">Replit</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u6c29355a\" id=\"u6c29355a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">是同类产品中的另一款优秀产品。与许多抽象大量幕后机制的 AI 开发工具不同，Replit 可以查看文件结构、添加和创建文件，总体感觉控制力更强。Replit 似乎将协作功能融入其中，如果您是与开发人员或其他团队成员合作的设计师，这将非常实用。我非常欣赏 Replit 的任务功能。它会建议可以添加到项目范围中的功能或项目，这有助于我在首次提示和原型设计时思考想要实现的结果。Replit 的一个小细节让我很欣赏，那就是它在项目编译过程中会显示提示——作为一个喜欢边写代码边学习的人，我很感激它能教会我一些最佳实践之类的知识。最后，Replit 最棒的功能是它的应用程序！如果您有一个大型项目或正在处理一些业余工作，这款应用程序可以在AI完成工作时通知您，以便您进行多任务处理。事实上，这款应用程序让您可以轻松地在移动设备上进行创作——如果您在旅途中突然有灵感，或者不在常用的办公地点附近，这款应用程序将是您的理想之选。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ued85d8f6\" id=\"ued85d8f6\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1756041309282-02a98ccd-1e49-4d97-bcc4-bed26c50b65d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u92781fca-c425-47ba-808f-f9231ef4b5a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u78afaade-908e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A336%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A143149%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A672%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22TODOTRACKER%20%E9%97%A8%20TODO%20LIST%20APP%20DEVELOPMENT%20PLANNING%20INITIAL%20VERSION%20INITIAT%20PLANNING%20PLAN%20APPROVAL%20VISUAL%20PREVIEW%20INTERACTIVE%20PROTOTYPE%20LATER%20WOULD%20YOU%20LIKE%20ANY%20OF%20THESE%20ADDITIONAL%20FEATURES%3FWE%20CAN%20ALSO%20MAKE%20CHANGES%20LATER.%20TASK%20CATEGORIES%2FTAGS%20DUE%20DATES%20AND%20REMINDERS%20TASK%20PRIORITY%20LEVELS%20SHARING%2FCOLLABORATION%20FEATURES%20APPROVE%20PLAN%20%26%20START%20MESSAGE%20AGENT...%200%20HAVE%20FEEDBACK%3F%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A70%2C%22y%22%3A18%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%22TODOTRACKER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A412%2C%22y%22%3A51%2C%22width%22%3A21%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E9%97%A8%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A596%2C%22y%22%3A55%2C%22width%22%3A196%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22TODO%20LIST%20APP%20DEVELOPMENT%20PLANNING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A433%2C%22y%22%3A102%2C%22width%22%3A99%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22INITIAL%20VERSION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A460%2C%22y%22%3A140%2C%22width%22%3A94%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22INITIAT%20PLANNING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A462%2C%22y%22%3A174%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22PLAN%20APPROVAL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A463%2C%22y%22%3A208%2C%22width%22%3A88%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22VISUAL%20PREVIEW%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A460%2C%22y%22%3A242%2C%22width%22%3A131%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22INTERACTIVE%20PROTOTYPE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A432%2C%22y%22%3A295%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22LATER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A433%2C%22y%22%3A327%2C%22width%22%3A496%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%22WOULD%20YOU%20LIKE%20ANY%20OF%20THESE%20ADDITIONAL%20FEATURES%3FWE%20CAN%20ALSO%20MAKE%20CHANGES%20LATER.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A461%2C%22y%22%3A364%2C%22width%22%3A128%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22TASK%20CATEGORIES%2FTAGS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A461%2C%22y%22%3A388%2C%22width%22%3A156%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22DUE%20DATES%20AND%20REMINDERS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A460%2C%22y%22%3A415%2C%22width%22%3A114%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22TASK%20PRIORITY%20LEVELS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A460%2C%22y%22%3A440%2C%22width%22%3A190%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22SHARING%2FCOLLABORATION%20FEATURES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A826%2C%22y%22%3A482%2C%22width%22%3A129%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22APPROVE%20PLAN%20%26%20START%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A423%2C%22y%22%3A572%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22MESSAGE%20AGENT...%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A421%2C%22y%22%3A606%2C%22width%22%3A15%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%220%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A851%2C%22y%22%3A606%2C%22width%22%3A88%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22HAVE%20FEEDBACK%3F%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23141c2d%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u12d41efd%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u55c33476\" id=\"u55c33476\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2eab81ed\" id=\"u2eab81ed\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">Replit 中的任务</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"rkAiq\" id=\"rkAiq\"><span data-lake-id=\"u053ef144\" id=\"u053ef144\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">控制力最强——Cursor</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u7f956d39\" id=\"u7f956d39\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubccf09e0\" id=\"ubccf09e0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">使用</span><a href=\"https://www.cursor.com/en\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u7d1b83b0\" id=\"u7d1b83b0\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubcebe5e7\" id=\"ubcebe5e7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">Cursor</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u190b3ef7\" id=\"u190b3ef7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">有点像跳进深渊。它能让你最大程度地掌控你的创作。它是一个代码编辑器，因此你可以完全控制安装软件包并根据自己的喜好编辑代码。但随之而来的是破坏代码的可能！正因如此，Cursor 一直是我最有成就感的工具，但也是最令人沮丧的工具。Cursor 是我工作流程的核心部分，随着上述更多产品与 GitHub 集成，我可以更轻松地在其他一些产品中开始创作（比如把粘土扔到轮子上），初步成型，然后在 Cursor 中完全塑造出我喜欢的最终形态。例如，我最近一直在开发一款冥想应用，我在 Figma 中创建了概念，在 Lovable 中构建完成，然后转到 Cursor。在 Cursor 中，我可以完全编辑用于引导用户呼吸的屏幕动画。总而言之，我强烈推荐 Cursor。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u09058caf\" id=\"u09058caf\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1756041309613-0899f416-616a-4133-abcd-3f356b4517c0.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9755ffbe-2eb9-448f-9d92-7b773d37a6b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%2