22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%2203%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1241%2C%22y%22%3A627%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%22REJECT%20AT%40%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1311%2C%22y%22%3A628%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22ACCEPT%20A%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A910%2C%22y%22%3A628%2C%22width%22%3A57%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22GENERATING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A416%2C%22y%22%3A655%2C%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%2204-MINI%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A921%2C%22y%22%3A661%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22ADD%20CONTEXT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A591%2C%22y%22%3A684%2C%22width%22%3A76%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22%2B%20ADD%20MODEL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A904%2C%22y%22%3A684%2C%22width%22%3A165%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22PLAN%2CSEARCH%2CBUILD%20ANYTHING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A16%2C%22y%22%3A695%2C%22width%22%3A66%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22NOTEPADS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A716%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22OUTLINE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A912%2C%22y%22%3A721%2C%22width%22%3A108%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22OO%20AGENT%20XI%20.%20AUTO%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A20%2C%22y%22%3A737%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22TIMELINE%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23191919%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u4c211874%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufb1d1546\" id=\"ufb1d1546\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u45101d09\" id=\"u45101d09\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">游标模型</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u38a9f7ee\" id=\"u38a9f7ee\"><em><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uda957d2b\" id=\"uda957d2b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">💡</span></strong></em><em><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u020236e9\" id=\"u020236e9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\"> 提示</span></strong></em><em><span data-lake-id=\"u8437ab1e\" id=\"u8437ab1e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">：默认情况下，Cursor 会自动选择模型，但您可以尝试使用特定模型。我发现这样更容易学习它的工作原理，并且在进行振动编码时可以获得更可预测的结果。我一直在使用 Sonnet 3.7，但最近我发现自己开始使用 Gemini 2.5，因为它似乎能更好地处理我的提示，而且用户界面也更简洁一些。</span></em></p><p data-lake-id=\"u551c386a\" id=\"u551c386a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u813b905f\" id=\"u813b905f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这就是我的氛围编码指南……暂时如此！正如我一开始提到的，这个领域涌现出如此多的工具——远超我一篇文章所能涵盖的范围。我非常期待尝试 Figma 的 Make——表面上看，把我所有的工作流程工具都集中到一个地方听起来是个好主意，但我很好奇效果会如何。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc13013ac\" id=\"uc13013ac\"><span data-lake-id=\"u29fb68a9\" id=\"u29fb68a9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: currentcolor; background-color: #FBDE28\">作为一名设计师，跟上时代步伐可能感觉很艰难。这几乎让人不知所措，但同时也让人无比兴奋。在这个任何人都可以创造任何东西的时代，对精湛技艺、精益求精和以用户为中心的理念的需求比以往任何时候都更加迫切。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7cd091a7\" id=\"u7cd091a7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u832933d5\" id=\"u832933d5\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">我们如何有意识地塑造想法？</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u83d9d3cb\" id=\"u83d9d3cb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u258d81b6\" id=\"u258d81b6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">我们如何让体验更加直观？</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue8663776\" id=\"ue8663776\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaa852fcf\" id=\"uaa852fcf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">我们如何将粘土放入轮子并制作出人们喜爱的东西？</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc475ea01\" id=\"uc475ea01\"><span data-lake-id=\"u74c746cd\" id=\"u74c746cd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">许多设计机构也面临着许多工作。您如何让您的设计师团队做好准备，迎接氛围编码？随着我们加快原型交付速度，如何确保适当的研究水平仍然能够指导和评估我们的工作？</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uda2f6c15\" id=\"uda2f6c15\"><span data-lake-id=\"u391a2b42\" id=\"u391a2b42\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这些产品并不能神奇地修复断裂的流程或协作。事实上，它们可能会加剧已存在的缺陷。缺乏清晰度的速度将比以往任何时候都更快地加深失调。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u42d27d21\" id=\"u42d27d21\"><span data-lake-id=\"u670e4b3f\" id=\"u670e4b3f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这些是我正在思考的一些事情，在接下来的几个月里，我一定会写出来。如果你一直在探索氛围编码领域，我很想听听你的经验。你有什么建议、工具或工作流程值得我参考吗？</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6fa5d0e2\" id=\"u6fa5d0e2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4a022e04\" id=\"u4a022e04\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">​</span><br></p><blockquote data-lake-id=\"u55c2fc4c\" id=\"u55c2fc4c\"><p data-lake-id=\"ub2462131\" id=\"ub2462131\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud9472953\" id=\"ud9472953\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://medium.com/@matthewpointon/the-designers-guide-to-vibe-coding-tools-3654b47aac55\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u5a2d0001\" id=\"u5a2d0001\"><span data-lake-id=\"u47cd7473\" id=\"u47cd7473\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://medium.com/@matthewpointon/the-designers-guide-to-vibe-coding-tools-3654b47aac55</span></a></p></blockquote>"}
